Title: Duplicate Advisory: Microsoft Security Advisory CVE-2025-55248: .NET Information Disclosure Vulnerability
Description:
### Duplicate Advisory
This advisory has been withdrawn because it is a duplicate of GHSA-gwq6-fmvp-qp68. This link is maintained to preserve external references.

### Original Description
Inadequate encryption strength in .NET, .NET Framework, Visual Studio allows an authorized attacker to disclose information over a network.
NotImpacted: All versions before 9.0.0, all versions starting from 9.0.10
